{%- comment -%}
  K&A Visit Us — Arrival (hero). Docs/store-location-build-spec.md
  Section 3 ("Section 1 — Arrival"), built from Prototypes/store-
  location-v1.html §SECTION 1, v2.1 (approved by Suraj).

  Deliberately built with NO photography — same judgment call as the
  approved prototype: no real atelier interior photography exists yet
  (see ka-visit-photo.liquid for the separate, explicitly-temporary
  placeholder used further down the page). Reusing garment photography
  here to imply "this is our space" would be a trust risk the spec
  explicitly avoids (Section 2). Kept as an engraved-invitation moment
  — dark ground, a bordered card, a CSS-only woven texture — instead.

  Entry motion: pure CSS keyframes with staggered delays (fadeIn/fadeUp,
  shared in ka-animations.css), not the sitewide .reveal/IntersectionObserver
  mechanism — this section is fully in-viewport on load, so a scroll-
  triggered reveal would never fire. Same reasoning already documented
  in ka-about-hero.liquid / ka-diary-coming-soon.liquid.

  Nav note: unlike the flat HTML prototype (which floats a transparent
  nav over this dark hero and crystallises it on scroll), this page's
  real ka-nav.liquid instance renders permanently "settled" (opaque)
  here, same as every other non-homepage template including About Us
  — About Us also opens on a dark hero and gets the same settled nav.
  This is an already-established sitewide convention (see ka-nav.liquid
  is_home comment), not a fidelity gap specific to this page.
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="ka-visit-arrival" aria-label="Visit the K&amp;A Atelier">
  <div class="ka-visit-arrival__card">
    <div class="ka-visit-arrival__mark"></div>
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--on-dark ka-visit-arrival__eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 class="ka-visit-arrival__title">
      {{ section.settings.title_line1 }}
      <strong>{{ section.settings.title_line2 }}</strong>
    </h1>
    <p class="ka-visit-arrival__sub">{{ section.settings.subtitle }}</p>
    <div class="ka-visit-arrival__cta">
      <a
        href="{{ section.settings.google_maps_url | default: 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/tU41xSkVonr4Qe8v9' }}"
        class="btn-ghost"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        {{ section.settings.cta_label }}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Visit — Arrival",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "text", "id": "eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Santacruz West, Mumbai" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "title_line1", "label": "Title line 1 (italic)", "default": "The Atelier" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "title_line2", "label": "Title line 2 (roman, small)", "default": "Mumbai" },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subtitle",
      "default": "A real address, a fitting mirror, and the quiet particular to a house where every piece is made once, for one person. Walk in, or write ahead — either way, we're glad to have you."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "CTA"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_label", "label": "CTA label", "default": "Get Directions" },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "google_maps_url",
      "label": "Google Maps link",
      "info": "Defaults to K&A's real Google Business listing (maps.app.goo.gl/tU41xSkVonr4Qe8v9)."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "Visit — Arrival" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
